title: MYB
description: This is a randomly ordered feed of the most recent entries from MYB, skipping any feeds with errors.

items.title: The Housemaid 2 ‘Guaranteed’ By Its Star After Becoming A Box Office Smash
items.description: The Housemaid is turning into a box office hit and as such, The Housemaid 2 seems likely. Not likely, but guaranteed, according to one of its stars.

items.title: Cop Transforms Into Frog According To AI Generated Police Report
items.description: An AI police report tool turned a cop into a “frog,” exposing how generative AI in policing can warp reality.

items.title: Apple iPhone 18 May See A Sharp Price Increase, New Report Claims
items.description: The next iPhone could have a processor inside that’s a lot more expensive. Which will likely increase the price of the phone.

items.title: Apple Won’t Release iPhone 18 In 2026, New Report Claims
items.description: If you’re looking forward to buying the iPhone 18, it seems you’re going to have a long wait.

items.title: The ‘Stranger Things’ Finale Dethroned In Netflix’s Top 10 List By A New Show
items.description: Despite just airing a blockbuster finale, there's a new show that has unseated Stranger Things on the top of Netflix's top 10 list.
